cohort_name: [PP25 SgxHowOften] AKI with dialysis (no ESKD or prior dialysis)
logic_description: from cohortID362  with following changes: (1) change index to include broader defn dialysis + AKI (2) removal of Epo (3) Dialysis within 30d of index.  Note change #1 would address index date misspecification, but also ensure dialysis is for AKI (and not other indications) in general use; risk is that it may introduce immortal time bias via future criteria.   (3) change to no prior dialysis in 365 from chronic dialysis. (4) expanded AKI to include HRS, post partum.

cohort_name: [PP25 HowOftenSgx] AKI (condn or dialysis), no ESKD or dialysis in 365
logic_description: from cohortID 362 with following changes: (1) added broader dialysis defn with nested AKI condition occurrence in 7 d; (2) removal of Epo.  (1) expanded for broader network study applicability, AKI required for more general use (to eliminate cases of dialysis for non AKI indications).  This form would address index date misspecification (in case dialysis is index event), but possibly introduce immortal time bias (via requirement of future event). (3) changed to no prior dialysis in last 365 (from 'chronic' dialysis). (4) expanded AKI to include HRS, post partum
